Program Prot_evol, author Ugo Bastolla (CSIC-UAM) ubastolla@cbm.csic.es
It simulates protein evolution with selection on the thermodynamic stability of the folded state and the conservation of the native structure and it computes site-specific substitution matrices (frequencies and exchangeability) according to different structure- and stability-constrained models of protein evolution. It optionally performs simulations of protein evolution with stability constraints and predicts the stability change of all possible DNA mutations.

